videos.description: Big South Freshman of the Year Carlik Jones drives and finishes with a nice layup at the rim.
videos.headline: Jones drives and finishes for Radford

videos.description: Radford's Carlik Jones drives and kicks to Travis Fields Jr. in the corner for the triple.
videos.headline: Fields open for 3

videos.description: Carlik Jones spins and shoots a falling layup for the Highlanders that is swatted by Scottie James.
videos.headline: Liberty's James erases Radford layup

videos.description: Scottie James drains the triple to put Liberty within one of Radford.
videos.headline: Liberty fights back on James' 3

videos.description: Radford's Travis Fields Jr. drains the ice-cold 3-pointer as the shot clock sounds.
videos.headline: Fields beats shot clock with long triple

videos.description: Lovell Cabbil throws a beautiful cross-court pass to Ryan Kemrite who finds nothing but net from deep.
videos.headline: Kemrite money from 3

videos.description: Liberty's Scottie James navigates through traffic with a sweet up-and-under move to get the layup to fall.
videos.headline: James flies for up-and-under finish

videos.description: Carlik Jones shows why he was the Big South Conference Freshman of the Year with a game-winner from deep as time expires to defeat Liberty 55-52.
videos.headline: Buzzer-beater sends Radford to first NCAA tournament since 2009

videos.description: Carlik Jones' buzzer-beater punches Radford's ticket to the NCAA tournament for the first time since 2009 as the Highlanders top the Liberty Flames 55-52 in the Big South Final.
videos.headline: Radford wins in dramatic fashion
